<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Quality Digital Services</title>
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f2f4ff;
      /* padding: 20px; */
    }

   
header {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo img {
      width: 400px;
      height: 100px;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    .logo span {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .logo span b {
      color: #f90;
    }

    nav a {
      margin-left: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #ff6600;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .body-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .main-container {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      max-width: 1000px;
    }

    .info-card {
      flex: 2;
      background-color: #e8f1ff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .info-card h2 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #c60000;
    }

    .info-card h3 {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .info-card ul,
    .info-card ol {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .app-logo {
      width: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .form-card {
      flex: 1;
      background-color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .form-card h2 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    label {
      margin: 10px 0 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    input,
    select {
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 1px solid #aaa;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    button {
      padding: 12px;
      background-color: #f57c00;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #e06b00;
    }

    .continue-btn {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
   <header class="header">
    <a href="/dashboard"><div class="logo">
      <img src="image/Hiring_Poster1Artboard_8@4x[1](1).png"></div></a>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="/dashboard">Home</a>
      <a href="/careerneed">Careers</a>
      <a href="/logoutneed">Logout</a>
    </nav>
  </header>


  <main class="body-content">
    <div class="main-container">
      <section class="info-card">
        <img src="image/SBI IRCTC Credit Card.png" alt="IRCTC Credit Card" class="app-logo"/>
        <h2>SBI IRCTC Credit Card</h2>
        <li>India’s Favorite Card for Train Travelers</li>
        <h3>Key Benefits</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Save up to 10% Value Back on rail ticket purchases via IRCTC</li>
          <li>350 Bonus Reward Points on card activation</li>
          <li>Earn Reward Points every time you plan a trip</li>
          <li>1% waiver on transaction charges for bookings via <a href="https://www.irctc.co.in" target="_blank">irctc.co.in</a></li>
          <li>Applicable for AC1, AC2, AC3, and AC Chair Car ticket bookings</li>
          <li>Use IRCTC Mobile App (Android only) or website for maximum savings</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>How to Apply</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Click on Apply Now to start the application</li>
          <li>Fill in the required personal and financial details</li>
          <li>Submit the form and receive your application number</li>
          <li>Track your application using the reference number</li>
          <li>SBI Representative will contact you to complete verification and issuance process</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Who Can Apply?</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Age: 21–65 years</li>
          <li>Employment: Salaried or Self-employed</li>
          <li>Minimum Income: ₹20,000/month</li>
          <li>Credit Score: 700+ preferred</li>
          <li>Existing credit card holders are preferred</li>
          <li>Citizenship: Indian Citizens & NRIs</li>
        </ol>
        <h3>Terms & Conditions</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Up to 10% value back on eligible IRCTC bookings</li>
          <li>Bonus Reward Points on joining section</li>
          <li>Offers applicable only on select booking classes and payment channels</li>
          <li>Reward earning & redemption policies are subject to change without notice</li>
          <li>Standard SBI Card terms & conditions apply</li>
        </ol>
      </section>
    </div>

    <button class="continue-btn" onclick="location.href='/CSIB'" >Click here to Continue</button>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
